item.title: Prayer bpn10412 in Kiribati
item.description: Te Atua, ae Atuau! Kaotai moaia Am koraki ake a Tatangiriko ni koaua, ao buokiia ni barongaia anera n te tokanikai ae e koaua raoi. Kamatoai waeia i aon Kawaim ae e eti, ao man Am tituaraoi are mangkoa kauki i mwaaiia mataroan Am kakabwaia; bwa a kaakabanea i aon Kawaim baike Ko a tia n anganiia, n tararuaa Am Aro, ni katutuka aia mwioko i nanon aia Ururingko, n angaanga nanoia i bukin Tangiram, ma n aki tauanibwai ni kaubwaiia i bukin neboan Tamaroam, ao ni kakaaei aanga i bukin Kakukureiam.
